  "name": "Fires of the Aegean",
  "slug": "fires-of-the-aegean",
  "date": "September 30, 2025",
  "description": "This evening is a celebration of flame and freshness. Guests begin with shared mezze—dolmades, taramasalata, and grilled halloumi—before moving to fire-roasted seafood, lamb with rosemary smoke, and citrus-laced pastries. Throughout the night, Nikos shares stories of the sea and the vineyards that shaped his youth. The experience feels elemental, like sitting at a village table by the shore, yet heightened into something luxuriously theatrical.",
